      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "When the weight feels this heavy, the idea of simply letting go can feel like the only logical relief. If you are truly feeling that the fight is hopeless, please understand that there are people who want to help you through this overwhelming darkness. Reaching out to a crisis hotline or mental health professional is a safe way to talk about these final thoughts without judgment. You do not have to carry this immense burden alone; there is support available right now.",
